<p>The pizza sauce is also awesome.  One of my favorite topping combos is to roast vegetables and top the pizza with sauce, the veggies, feta and fresh oregano.  Leftover veggies get mixed with leftover sauce for roasted vegetable pasta sauce on another night.  More details and pizza grilling ideas are on my site: <a href="http://inkellyskitchen.wordpress.com/2010/04/13/pizza-you-will-fall-in-love-with/" rel="nofollow">http://inkellyskitchen.wordpress.com/2010/04/13/pizza-you-will-fall-in-love-with/</a></p>
